This is a web sample application.

The following concepts are used.

Spring Security (BASIC Authentication, Persistence backed Authorization, Moderate Security Hardening)
Spring Mvc (REST, Traditional MVC)
Spring Data (JPA)
Jdbc
Spring Integration Test (Junit)

The project is fully tested with integration tests, and runs in JBOSS 7 EAP

Links
(This assumes you have it running locally)
Simple Rest: Get http://localhost:8080/app/sample/1
Tip:  To set up users in JBOSS use the addUser script included with in JBOSS's home/bin directory